Eric Christian Olsen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eric_Christian_Olsen 0 Eric Christian Olsen (born May 31, 1977) is an American actor. He is known for his portrayals of Detective Marty Deeks on the CBS television series NCIS: Los Angeles, and of Austin in the film Not Another Teen Movie.
